genes.title: 项目概述
genes.content:
Ryu, a fork of Kuzu, is an Embedded Property Graph Database built for speed with vector search and full-text search built in. Implements Cypher.

来源: https://github.com/predictable-labs/ryugraph
语言: C++
Stars: 125

genes.title: 安装与快速开始
genes.content: Refer to our [Getting Started](https://ryugraph.io/docs/get-started/) page for your first example.
